column5: I planning a day trip to lake eugenia as i keep hearing it's full of buketheadsjust wondering if anyone has accurate directions to the actual boat launch?

....I'm not 100% certain but if memory serves me right it's located near the dam on the west side. According to a map I searched it's may be off Pellisier St. Which runs off Beaver Valley Road (Grey Rd. 13)
Steve has it.  BTW, where is Barb?
